    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In the visual arts refers to systematization of the individual properties of colors and of their complex interactions. For the historical theory of applying color, especially in Renaissance art theory, use "colorito."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
